<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 21:12:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加拿大法官下月辞去香港最高上诉法院职务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/canadian-judge-quit-hong-kong-top-appeals-court-next-month-2024-06-10/</link><description>香港最高上诉法院的一名加拿大法官周一宣布，她将于下个月任期届满后辞职，并表示她仍然对法院成员及其独立性充满信心。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/canadian-judge-quit-hong-kong-top-appeals-court-next-month-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>英国法官称香港法治“严重受损”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-rule-law-profoundly-compromised-says-british-judge-2024-06-10/</link><description>一位最近从香港最高上诉法院辞职的英国法官周一表示，在政府持有强烈意见的法律领域，香港的法治“严重受损”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-rule-law-profoundly-compromised-says-british-judge-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院小组扩大对宝马使用被禁中国供应商零部件的调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-senate-panel-expands-probe-into-bmw-use-parts-banned-chinese-supplier-2024-06-10/</link><description>参议院财政委员会主席周一表示，他正在扩大对德国汽车制造商宝马使用来自被禁中国供应商的电子元件的调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 14:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-senate-panel-expands-probe-into-bmw-use-parts-banned-chinese-supplier-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>古巴吸引俄罗斯人和中国人重振陷入困境的旅游业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/cuba-woos-russians-chinese-revive-ailing-tourist-sector-2024-06-10/</link><description>一个工作日的早晨，俄罗斯游客谢尔盖·博亚里什尼奇 (Serguei Boyaryshnic) 带着家人带着敬畏之心在哈瓦那旧城色彩柔和的建筑和鹅卵石街道中漫步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 11:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/cuba-woos-russians-chinese-revive-ailing-tourist-sector-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>大使表示，美国需要日本的帮助来提高军工生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-needs-japans-help-boost-military-production-ambassador-says-2024-06-10/</link><description>美国驻日本大使周一在两国启动军事工业合作谈判时表示，美国需要日本的帮助来应对欧洲和亚洲的战略挑战，这些挑战正给美国国防工业带来压力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 11:04:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-needs-japans-help-boost-military-production-ambassador-says-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：欧洲因马克龙提前大选呼吁而震动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-10/</link><description>塞缪尔·因迪克 (Samuel Indyk) 展望美国和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾逮捕乘快艇闯入台北港的中国男子</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-arrests-chinese-man-who-took-speedboat-into-taipei-harbour-2024-06-10/</link><description>台湾海岸警卫队周一表示，台湾逮捕了一名驾驶快艇进入通往台北的河口港口非法入境的中国男子。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 09:01:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-arrests-chinese-man-who-took-speedboat-into-taipei-harbour-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>莫迪第三任期回归，印度和巴基斯坦领导人诉诸X外交</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/pakistan-pm-congratulates-indias-modi-taking-oath-prime-minister-2024-06-10/</link><description>周一，在纳伦德拉·莫迪第三次宣誓就任总理的第二天，印度和巴基斯坦领导人通过 X 诉诸外交。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 08:10:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/pakistan-pm-congratulates-indias-modi-taking-oath-prime-minister-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将公布中国电动汽车关税税率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-set-disclose-tariff-rates-chinese-electric-vehicles-2024-06-10/</link><description>预计欧盟委员会本周将披露计划对中国电动汽车征收的关税，称其补贴过多，此举可能会引发北京方面的严厉言论并可能实施报复。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 06:14:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-set-disclose-tariff-rates-chinese-electric-vehicles-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>尽管欧盟正在考虑关税，但欧洲国家仍在争夺中国电动汽车工厂和就业机会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-nations-compete-chinese-ev-factories-jobs-even-eu-weighs-tariffs-2024-06-10/</link><description>欧洲各国政府可能对中国廉价电动汽车涌入其市场持谨慎态度，但他们也在激烈竞争新竞争对手带来的制造业投资和就业份额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 06:03:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-nations-compete-chinese-ev-factories-jobs-even-eu-weighs-tariffs-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>市场：美国如何鼓励世界寻找美元替代品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/market-how-us-is-daring-world-find-dollar-alternative-2024-06-10/</link><description>美国正在兴高采烈地削弱支撑美元作为世界储备货币的支柱，最新的打击来自一些有权势的美国人在唐纳德·特朗普被定罪后对法治提出质疑。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 05:03:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/market-how-us-is-daring-world-find-dollar-alternative-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰总理称中国总理李强本周将访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-pm-says-china-premier-li-qiang-visit-this-week-2024-06-10/</link><description>新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森周一表示，中国总理李强将于本周访问新西兰，这是中国总理七年来首次访华。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 04:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-pm-says-china-premier-li-qiang-visit-this-week-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国致力于针对朝鲜核威胁制定联合战略</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-hold-new-round-nuclear-planning-talks-seoul-2024-06-10/</link><description>官员们表示，韩国和美国高级国防官员周一在首尔会面，制定新的指导方针，以协调应对朝鲜的任何核威胁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 03:10:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-hold-new-round-nuclear-planning-talks-seoul-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>全球股指小幅上涨，欧元下跌，收益率上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-10/</link><description>摩根士丹利资本国际 (MSCI) 全球股市指数周一小幅走高，投资者等待美国关键通胀数据和央行政策会议，但法国总统马克龙宣布提前大选后欧元下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 02:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>马克龙呼吁提前举行法国大选，欧元暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-slips-one-month-low-macron-calls-french-election-2024-06-10/</link><description>周日欧洲议会选举中极右翼势力获胜促使法国总统马克龙提前举行全国大选，欧元周一下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 01:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-slips-one-month-low-macron-calls-french-election-2024-06-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>